{"tid":522362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慾妻常逼上床 丈夫累癱請求離婚","createTime":"2018-01-07T13:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T05:19:45.000Z","uid":35468,"like":234,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"2f4a182a20c5ae121e3647213f88d1bdb86dd980","tid":522362,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"慾妻常逼上床 運將累癱訴離獲准<br />\n<strong>2018/01/04 </strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20180104/37893187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fheadline%2Fdaily%2F20180104%2F37893187&d=iDv%2F7x6hUhJR8ARk1BOsyjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=01302eb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fheadline%2Fdaily%2F20180104%2F37893187&h=c7f8beea\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20180104/37893187</a><br />\n<br />\n【突發中心╱桃園報導】一名陳姓貨車司機因為工作勞累，回家倒頭就睡，無奈妻子性慾特別強，常常逼他上床「履行義務」，貨車司機多次拒絕，為此妻子發生嚴重爭吵，幾次勉強應付，但隔天精神不濟，無力工作，還被僱主訓斥、同事譏笑，兩年後終於受不了妻子需求，提出離婚訴訟，上月底法院判准離婚。<br />\n<br />\n女疑男方有小三<br />\n<br />\n法院審理時，妻子完全不接受先生說法，懷疑丈夫可能有小三，才會再三推諉「房事」，她認為要求行房並不過分，這是對方應盡的義務，妻子更指稱，陳男常常不回家，還曾載女同事出遊，追問時陳男支吾其詞，甚至不願多做解釋，態度傲慢，讓她精神痛苦不已，就是因懷疑先生在外亂來，才會要求盡丈夫的責任，不認為據此可作為離婚的理由。<br />\n<br />\n陳男在法庭裡否認對婚姻不忠，強調因工作勞累，並非妻子所言在外有小三。雖然兩人各說各話，但法官審理時發現，兩人在調解時仍互相爭吵、劍拔弩張，誰也不讓誰，互相憎恨也無意繼續經營婚姻，早已喪失夫妻應有的互信基礎，破綻已無法修復，因此判准離婚。 <br />\n<br />\n台灣新聞所以用「小三」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好屌我"},{"pid":"319b3442a0b73b8520ae1a31c2ebf180e7781c9a","tid":522362,"uid":47359,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">快</span>"},{"pid":"78ad0e61756cb4c0cdfa3c49a52c60ca262f6b56","tid":522362,"uid":10325,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"未有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9175af54eded856d1830bd930c0640db0e86736","tid":522362,"uid":57835,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:21:05.000Z","msg":"要求行房並不過分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe90c78ff41f1f5bc88d4d438f5a064406d19f4","tid":522362,"uid":76115,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:24:28.000Z","msg":"#NoMeansNo<br />\n#MeToo<br />\n#DontBlameTheVictim"},{"pid":"83c7d9890c4c8afc0f2afc2b349a1c923da27ea0","tid":522362,"uid":121393,"like":275,"dislike":8,"score":267,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/212443_5ca2d2643131ca23694502494d1ccdb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F212443_5ca2d2643131ca23694502494d1ccdb6.jpg&h=9c93a863&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e377fc92ec198c42a6a937c7cf212b02c3af0ef","tid":522362,"uid":47359,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"83c7d9890c4c8afc0f2afc2b349a1c923da27ea0","tid":522362,"uid":121393,"like":275,"dislike":8,"score":267,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/212443_5ca2d2643131ca23694502494d1ccdb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F212443_5ca2d2643131ca23694502494d1ccdb6.jpg&h=9c93a863&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:25:39.000Z","msg":"絕對有講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa58d654bc8008ab7afcd5b5162d647cc7d1f15","tid":522362,"uid":82382,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"快點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb374663993ba988fbb9c76b7e6459536ecae4b","tid":522362,"uid":158323,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"7fa58d654bc8008ab7afcd5b5162d647cc7d1f15","tid":522362,"uid":82382,"like":3,"disli